<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-05-11T18:12:28-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-05-11T18:12:28-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T18:12:28-04:00</updated><title> Steam、Epic 和 GMG 取消非 PSN 国家的《对马岛之魂》PC 预订</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;对马岛之魂的屏幕截图，显示一个角色俯瞰田野，背景是丘陵和山脉。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ydpUm-5qwgcVccbLngiYvVzt0Vs=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73341722/Ghost_of_Tsushima_Director_s_Cut_W全部纸.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;屏幕截图：&lt;em>;对马之魂&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;052Lal&quot;>;据报道，Steam、Epic 和 Green Man Gaming 正在取消 PC 预购并退款&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24092291/ghost-of-tsushima-directors-cut-pc-release-date-steam&quot;>;&lt;em>;对马之魂的港口&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;对于居住在 170 多个国家/地区无法访问 PlayStation 网络的买家，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.eurogamer.net/ghost-of-tsushima-directors-cut-pc-players- are-getting-auto-refunds-if-they-cannot-legally-sign-up-for-psn&quot;>;报告&lt;em>;Eurogamer&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。尽管事实上，可以说游戏中最重要的部分仍然可以在没有 PlayStation Network 帐户链接的情况下玩。该消息是在 Valve &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/games/2024/5/10/24153281/uhhh-anything-you-want-to-tell-us-about-ghost-of- tsushimas-psn-requirement-on-pc-sony&quot;>;昨天突然在这些国家下架了该游戏&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Pxvu7m&quot;>;&lt;em>;对马岛之魂&lt;/em>;仅需要 PSN 帐户链接才能进行传奇多人游戏模式，而单人战役则不受此要求，游戏开发者已超出其规定&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/SuckerPunchProd/status/1786462939748384943&quot;>;在最近的帖子中说&lt;/a>;。 Steam、Green Man Gaming 和 Epic Games Store 都发布了同样的免责声明。理论上，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154412/steam-refunding-ghost-of-tsushima-preorders-psn-网络不可用&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154412/steam-refunding-ghost-of-tsushima-preorders-psn-network-unavailable" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154412/steam-refunding-ghost-of-tsushima-preorders-psn-network-unavailable</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-11T14:20:39-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T14:20:39-04:00</updated><title> OpenAI 可能很快就会推出多模式人工智能数字助理</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;OpenAI 徽标的演绎，看起来像一个风格化的漩涡。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/uclea2XDI37W1Jxf9FgUgJ9KH7o=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73341500/STK149_AI_03.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;6aJOYR&quot;>;OpenAI 已向一些客户展示了一种新的多模式 AI 模型，根据 &lt;来自 &lt;em>;The Information&lt; 的 href=&quot;https://www.theinformation.com/articles/openai-develops-ai-voice-assistant-as-it-chases-google-apple?rc=r6gev9&quot;>;新报告/em>;&lt;/a>;。该媒体援引未透露姓名的消息来源称，这可能是该公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153421/openai-chatgpt-google-search -competitor-service-io&quot;>;计划于周一展示&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XgPXkn&quot;>;据报道，与现有的单独转录相比，新模型可以更快、更准确地解释图像和音频文本转语音模型可以做到这一点。显然，它能够帮助客户服务代理“更好地理解呼叫者的语调，或者他们是否在讽刺”，并且“理论上”，该模型可以帮助学生学习数学或翻译现实世界的标志，写道&lt;em>;信息。&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XQF9wh&quot;>;该媒体的消息来源说...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/5/11/24154307/openai-multimodal-digital-assistant-chatgpt-phone-calls&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154307/openai-multimodal-digital-assistant-chatgpt-phone-calls" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154307/openai-multimodal-digital-assistant-chatgpt-phone-calls</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-11T12:05:16-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T12:05:16-04:00</updated><title> The Verge 2024 年母亲节礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;热气球携带各种母亲节礼物的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/drF8sxK2oKQSKl03XYlOd9EAgZ8=/0x0:1750x1167/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73290208/247058_Mothers_Day_Gift_Guide_ML ouart.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Manon Louart 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;我们发现了一系列独特的礼物创意，超越了通常主宰日常的鲜花和巧克力。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24115101/best-mothers-day-gift-ideas-2024-mom-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24115101/best-mothers-day-gift-ideas-2024-mom-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24115101/best-mothers-day-gift-ideas-2024-mom-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-11T11:37:46-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T11:37:46-04:00</updated><title> iFixit 的 Pro Tech Toolkit 特价仅 60 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/a7uikWe02BUPNdFqhoZxG73YsAs=/0x0:1200x800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73341296 /iFixit_Pro_Tech_Toolkit_Lifestyle_Press_Image.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;iFixit 的升级工具包包含各种小零件，所有这些都可以很好地插入箱子中，并包含织物卷。&lt;/em>; |图片：iFixit&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;CrMGYr&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/28/23738770/right-to-repair-updates -laws&quot;>;维修权运动&lt;/a>;取得了一些重大胜利&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23951200/right-to-repair-law-apple-ifixit-iphone&quot; >;过去几年&lt;/a>;，诸如&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/28/23738770/right-to-repair-updates-laws#stream-entry -cedcdb35-6e12-4ebc-9909-e3cbe9b58147&quot;>;加利福尼亚州&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/6/3/23153504/right-to-repair-new-york -state-law-ifixit-repairability-diy&quot;>;纽约&lt;/a>;和&lt;a h