ple Vision Pro&lt;/a>;，以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifixit.com%2FNews%2F95474%2Frabbit-r1-and- humane-ai-pin-teardown-the-beginning- of-a-new-device-category&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F5%2F11%2F24153242%2Fifixit-pro-tech-toolkit-sharge-retro- 67-charger-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;人性化 AI Pin&lt;/a>;（抱歉，不抱歉）。也就是说，该公司还...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24153242/ifixit-pro-tech-toolkit-sharge-retro -67-charger-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24153242/ifixit-pro-tech-toolkit-sharge-retro-67-charger-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24153242/ifixit-pro-tech-toolkit-sharge-retro-67-charger-deal-sale</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-11T11:16:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T11:16:00-04:00</updated><title> 2024 年 Google I/O 大会将再次聚焦人工智能</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google I/O 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xoUvQ6qgD35kbTQRRQB1b9HqUuk=/0x120:5000x3453/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73341268/Google_IO.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Google&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Cg7qQ2&quot;>;Google 正准备在下周举办年度 Google I/O 开发者大会，自然&lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24152977/android-ai-google-io-2024-gemini&quot;>;一切都与人工智能有关&lt;/a>;。该公司对此毫不掩饰。自去年的 I/O 大会以来，它&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/6/23990466/google-gemini-llm-ai-model&quot;>;首次亮相了 Gemini&lt;/a>;，其新的、更强大的模型旨在与 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 竞争，并且一直在深入测试搜索、谷歌地图和 Android 的新功能。今年预计会听到很多有关这些内容的信息。&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;Wp6tYa&quot;>;Google I/O 何时举行以及您可以在哪里观看&lt;/h2>; &lt;p id=&quot;LhM9hD&quot;>;Google I/ O 将于 5 月 14 日星期二上午 10 点（太平洋时间）/下午 1 点（东部时间）进行主题演讲。您可以在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://io.google/2024/&quot;>;Google 网站&lt;/a>; 或其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEzRZ35urlk&amp;amp ;list=PLnKtcw5mIGUR2LxEdwDttuWXoGWZnfoOE&amp;amp;index=1&quot;>;YouTube 频道&lt;/a>;，通过也嵌入此页面顶部的直播链接。 （还有一个&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/live/6rP2rEWsfpM?si=EtDa4cg80T_H9mfz&quot;>;带有美国手语翻译器&lt;/a>;的版本。）设置...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154219/google-io-2024-what-to-expect-where-watch-livestream-ai-android-search-双子座&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154219/google-i-o-2024-what-to-expect-where-watch-livestream-ai-android-search-gemini" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154219/google-io-2024-what-to-expect-where-watch-livestream-ai-android-search-gemini</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-11T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title> 《Crow Country》是 90 年代生存恐怖游戏的华丽、肮脏的复兴</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;电子游戏《Crow Country》的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KxV1gDwDtEpOQ5uzemG4L-4D5XM=/0x0:3240x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73341148/Crow_Country_screenshot_09_Spindle.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：SFB Games&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zz8BYP&quot;>;即使现代恐怖游戏变得&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2017/1/ 23/14353714/resident-evil-7-biohazard-review-ps4-xbox-one-pc&quot;>;令人不安的身临其境&lt;/a>;，仍然有一个地方可以体现老式生存恐怖的特殊氛围。通过肮脏的视觉效果、神秘的谜题、缓慢的节奏和笨拙的控制的组合，PlayStation 时代的游戏，如《生化危机》和《寂静岭》，能够营造出一种独特的紧张气氛和恐怖。如果这种游戏永远不会过时，&lt;em>;Crow Country&lt;/em>;就是这样的情况。它具有经典的外观和感觉，但又具有恰到好处的现代气息。这是经典恐怖片的完美演绎。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;2lLpM0&quot;>;&lt;em>;Crow Country&lt;/em>; 来自独立工作室 SFB Games，由 Tom 和 Adam Vian 兄弟领导，迄今为止，该工作室已成功创建相当不拘一格的版本库。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2017/11/10/16633946/snipperclips-plus-nintendo-switch-interview&quot;>;有趣的 Switch 发布...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24153478/crow-country-review-steam-ps5-xbox&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24153478/crow-country-review-steam-ps5-xbox" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24153478/crow-country-review-steam-ps5-xbox</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-11T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> AI时代的Android</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;绿色和蓝色背景上的 Android 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gtVDQqztRhjiwAmIK--PNXNTQmc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73341040/acastro_STK112_android_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Google 年度开发者大会将于周二开幕。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;KEEyOv&quot;>;过去几个月让一件事变得非常清晰：&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /4/21/24134967/ai-gadgets- humane-pin-android-pixel-gemini&quot;>;手机保持不败&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;OT8G1x&quot;>;本应拯救的人工智能小工具我们通过手机&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24126502/ humane-ai-pin-review&quot;>;不幸地&lt;/a>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/5/2/24147159/rabbit-r1-review-ai-gadget&quot;>;未成熟&lt;/a>;——无论我们抱有什么样的幻想，Humane AI pin 或 Rabbit R1 都会提供任何类型的药膏&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24119076/ios-android-notifications-focus-modes-scheduled-summary&quot;>;处理个人技术的持续烦恼&lt;/a>;已经消失。热门小工具春季已经结束，开发者季节即将来临，从 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/14/24101171/google-io-2024-announced-may-14-android 开始-ai-gemini&quot;>;本周二的 Google I/O&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;0OidrN&quot;>;这也恰好是 Android 的关键时刻。 I/O 紧随&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/18/24133881/google-android-pixel-teams-reorg-rick-osterloh&quot;>;一次重大重新发布之后org&lt;/a>; 首次将 Android 团队与 Google 硬件团队合并在一起。指令很明确：全速前进，在更多事情上投入更多人工智能。不喜欢 Google...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24152977/android-ai-google-io-2024-gemini&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24152977/android-ai-google-io-2024-gemini" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24152977/android-ai-google-io-2024-gemini</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-11T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-11T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Garmin Lily 2 是我度假时需要的追踪器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在彩色背景上关闭丁香 Garmin Lily 2 Sport&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ytls7u_jff4G6E-tuQ9QKKfJ1kk=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73341076/247019_Garmin_Lily_2_AKrales_0014.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Lily 2 是一款小巧、低调的跟踪器，适合休闲用户。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;它的局限性使其在日常生活中表现不佳，但最终在试图与世界脱节时成为一个优势。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24152258/garmin-lily-2-fitness-tracker-wearable-smartwatch&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24152258/garmin-lily-2-fitness-tracker-wearable-smartwatch" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24152258/garmin-lily-2-fitness-tracker-wearable-smartwatch</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-10T19:14:07-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-10T19:14:07-04:00</updated><title>凝视戴尔泄露的高通 X Elite 笔记本电脑</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;戴尔笔记本电脑背靠背浮动并打开显示纤薄，绿色壁纸屏幕带有气球，底部键盘行有副驾驶键&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn .com/thumbor/dWt_9ym2Hov4biu0ekdVaon7xtk=/0x0:3707x2471/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73340420/Screenshot_2024_05_10_at_4.24.16_PM.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;fi gcaption>;&lt;em>;这太瘦了XPS。&lt;/em>; |图片：Windows Report&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;t2wH9t&quot;>;想看看戴尔的新笔记本电脑系列，该系列显然由高通即将推出的产品提供支持&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24107331 /qualcomm-gdc-2024-snapdragon-on-windows-games&quot;>;Snapdragon X Elite&lt;/a>; 处理器？ &lt;a href=&quot;https://windowsreport.com/exclusive-images-this-is-dells-upcoming-lineup-with-elite-x-intel-ultra-cpus/&quot;>;由 Windows 报告提供&lt;/ em>;&lt;/a>;，这些泄露的图片早于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/18/24104982/microsoft-ai-event-build-2024-satya-nadella&quot; >;微软 5 月 20 日的活动，其中新 Surface&lt;/a>;（以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/7/24151329/asus-will-announce-an-ai-pc-the -same-day-as-microsoft&quot;>;其他笔记本电脑&lt;/a>;）预计将配备相同的芯片。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;C4P8ZH&quot;>;毫不奇怪，它们看起来像笔记本电脑 - 尽管整体外形更纤薄。&lt; /p>; &lt;p id=&quot;oTdSYr&quot;>;最有趣的型号是戴尔的新款 XPS 13 9345，它似乎是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23284276/dell- xps-13-plus-intel-2022-review&quot;>;2022 年的 XPS 13 Plus&lt;/a>;。它在顶行有相同的触摸条，并且仅配备两个用于 I/O 的 USB-C 端口。&lt; /p>; &lt;div>;&lt;div class=&quot;c-image-grid&quot;>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-image-grid__item&quot;>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图像：Windows 报告&lt;/cite >; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;戴尔 XPS 9345&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;/div>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-image-grid__item&quot;>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite >;图片：Windows 报告&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;戴尔 Inspiron 灵越 14 7441 Plus&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;/div>; &lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;HpAvjW &quot;>;还有一个泄露的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153897/dell-xps-qualcomm-snapdragon-x-elite -leak&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153897/dell-xps-qualcomm-snapdragon-x-elite-leak" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153897/dell-xps-qualcomm-snapdragon-x-elite-leak</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05